вңҸпёҸ Annotation Queue

https://langfuse.com/changelog/2024-10-10-annotation-queues

В 
Making human labelling of LLM outputs easier for teams is core to Langfuse.
Last week, we released Annotation Queues [https://langfuse.com/changelog/2024-10-10-annotation-queues]. Teams can now
collaboratively add scores using the Langfuse UI. You can score both traces and observations within a trace.
В 
вҶ’ Start setting up your human labelling workflow here [https://langfuse.com/docs/scores/annotation].
